data.description: Single-Level Home in East Medford with Spacious Backyard & Updated AmenitiesThis 3-bedroom home in East Medford is conveniently located near schools and shopping centers. As you enter, you're greeted by one of two lovely living spaces. Enjoy hosting dinner parties in the remodeled kitchen, which features newer appliances, or cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace on cooler days. The large backyard is perfect for outdoor activities and includes a play structure for kids. There's also plenty of space for RVs, boats and other toys. Recent updates include new flooring, paint, and HVAC ducting.
